50|$|<b>Cheque</b> <b>{{truncation}}</b> (check truncation in American English) is {{the conversion}} of a physical cheque into a substitute electronic form for transmission to the paying bank. <b>Cheque</b> <b>truncation</b> reduces or eliminates the physical movement of cheques and reduces the time and cost of processing the cheque clearance system. <b>Cheque</b> <b>truncation</b> also offers the potential reduction in settlement periods with the electronic processing of the cheque payment system.|$|E
