40|$|<b>Cheques</b> <b>Truncation</b> System {{can be used}} For {{the rapid}} {{clearing}} of <b>cheques.</b> <b>Cheques</b> <b>Truncation</b> System of the bank transmits the electronic version of cheque pictures to drawee branches for the payment through the clearinghouse. We are blindly trusting that the arrangement is very safe and insured. However, genuine information in the cheque image may be damaged and the quality may degrade or may duplicate by the intruders. In this work, Design and Implementation of watermarking technique using DWT-DCT for authentic, copyright protected and secured cheque transaction for CTS of the bank is discussed. In this work, it is implemented imperceptibility of watermark which are supported for copyright protection and security of cheque images...|$|R
