50|$|<b>Cheque</b> <b>Truncation</b> System (CTS) or Image-based Clearing System (ICS), in India, is {{a project}} of the Reserve Bank of India (RBI), commencing in 2010, for faster {{clearing}} of cheques. CTS {{is based on a}} <b>cheque</b> <b>truncation</b> or online image-based cheque clearing system where cheque images and magnetic ink character recognition (MICR) data are captured at the collecting bank branch and transmitted electronically.|$|E
